Visited @dobaraaindia in Phoenix Palladium mall at Lower Parel  for dinner and had the most wholesome experience! 🫶
The guest are greeted and served by specially abled people which is the most purest thing I have ever seen . They were literally the sweetest💖 
The concept of giving an employment to the specially abled people makes my heart smile🥺
The food is absolutely delicious 🤤
The ambiance gave me major fifa vibes😍 
They also have unplugged night on Every Tuesday 

Y’all definitely need to visit this restaurant to experience warm hospitality and immense gratitude towards little things in life💖
Thankyou so much for hosting me @dobaraaindia 
@rainmakerconsults can’t wait to visit again 🥺🥺

Just wanted to share this 
I recently went to judge a Fashion show for @sea_town2022 fest at Lala Lajpat Rai College  for the very first time and I can’t put into words of how proud I’m.🧿🧿
From being a tomboy in my school days, to not getting selected for Fashion show because of my height in my college days to finally being the JUDGE🙌 
I’m upgrading and leveling up everyday 
I’m experiencing real growth, I’ve learnt one thing that is the moment when you start focusing on yourself , things start falling into place .🤍
I’m becoming the best version of myself and I’m proud of it💖🧿

Just wanna thank @sea_town2022 @llrc.official @nidhi.rajpurohit__  for giving me this huge opportunity ✨

• Visit the expo.

The Reflexes Game is so fun, that you just want to keep playing it again and again. And getting a caricature of yourself is the perfect end to a perfect day. So, in addition to getting your bib, visit the @idfcfirstbank 
Booth for an amazing experience!
